text: <!channel> Our friend (and newest tenant) Gino Reyes Borges has brought us a pecan pie to greet us. He's sitting next to Phillip in the new space. Come say hello and eat some pie! (The pie will be in the new kitchen).

<!channel>: There's a scoop of sorbet & gingersnap cookies in the freezer of the new fridge, courtesy of clarklewis. Would go well with a slice of pie. Just sayin'.  (It's in a white pint container). First come, first served.
<!channel>: there is also an actual ton of raspberry gelato in the new freezer. Probably not very good with pecan pie, but someone should eat it.
<!channel> I need to hijack our printer for a few minutes. If you need to print anything please wait until this is done. Will send another msg when the printer is free again.
<!channel> You may use the printer now.
